'''Wayne Stevens''' (born June 19, 1936) is an American former professional [[basketball]] player.<ref name=bbr>[http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/s/stevewa01.html Wayne Stevens]. basketball-reference.com. Retrieved on May 16, 2013.</ref> Stevens was selected in the [[1958 NBA Draft]] by the [[Cincinnati Royals]] after a collegiate career at the [[University of Cincinnati]].<ref name=bbr/> He played for the Royals in just eight games during the beginning of the [[1959<U+2013>60 NBA season]] and averaged 1.6 points, 2.0 rebounds and 0.5 assists per game.<ref name=bbr/>

